item.title: CVE-2022-4391|2024-08-03T01:41:44.485Z -- unknown -- vision%20interactive%20for%20wordpress
item.description: The Vision Interactive For WordPress plugin through 1.5.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow users such as contributor+ to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed.
